        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'You know Rosetta\\'s preferences by heart, and you\\'re well aware that fortune-telling cards aren\\'t exactly standard card-game material. Still, you just can\\'t help messing with her a bit.'}"
    },
